{"type": "article", "id": 8269, "title": "Wayfarer Fleck 太阳镜", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-09T07:30:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234636TES2JNruwZm9UeRX.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tRay-Ban 最近为其旗下 Wayfarer 太阳镜推出全新的 Fleck 系列，设计上采用经典迷人的玳瑁纹理，且采用多种配色，除了最普通的棕色以外，还有粉色，蓝色，绿色等。在镜片上，有吸光镜片和 B－15 偏光镜片两种选择，兼备实用和美貌。目前眼镜售价为 215 美元，<a href=\"www.ray-ban.com\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234634m6HdgWFL9shKENpu.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052346356nLqAoi7vMfzuC4a.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.53796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234635teC5vj2n4RJZgqYz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.53981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}